## Projects and entries (server actions)

1) Create project
- Use RPC create_project(owner_id, name, description) SECURITY DEFINER
- After success, revalidatePath('/dashboard') and redirect

2) Create entry
- Validate payload with zod (type, amount, unit, date)
- Insert row under current project
- Redirect to /projects/[id]?toast=entry_created

3) Member management
- Resolve user by email (via a helper RPC that returns a UUID)
- add_member(project_id, user_id, role) SECURITY DEFINER
- Editor can’t escalate roles; owner can

