## Evidence uploads

Client-side hashing (SHA-256)
- Use SubtleCrypto to compute hash (ArrayBuffer -> hex)
- Build filename: evidence/{project_id}/{hash}.{ext}
- Validate MIME/size before upload

Upload flow
- Upload to Supabase Storage with path above
- On success, server action inserts evidence_files row (hash, mime, size, file_path)
- UI displays preview (images) or a download link

Security
- Storage policies ensure only project members can read files within their project_id path portion
- Write (insert/delete) restricted to editor/owner

