## Troubleshooting playbook

- RLS “new row violates row-level security”
  - Check logged-in user context (auth.uid())
  - Verify membership in project_members
  - Ensure owner shortcuts are present
  - Avoid chaining policies that depend on each other’s results

- Storage “bucket not found”
  - Create the “evidence” bucket
  - Confirm correct path prefix “evidence/{project_id}”
  - Ensure storage policies match path pattern

- Next.js “workspace root inferred” warning
  - Remove duplicate lockfiles outside the project root
  - Or set turbopack.root or outputFileTracingRoot to __dirname

- Port 3000 in use
  - Run with a different port
  - Kill orphan node processes if necessary

- getLocale is not a function
  - Ensure getLocale is async and awaited in server components
  - Make sure export names match and you haven’t mixed old sync version

- “Export Button doesn’t exist…”
  - Confirm Button is exported in button.tsx
  - Confirm import path is "@/components/ui/button" and not default import

